text: For technical reasons, :P redirects here. For the emoticon, see emoticons. P is the sixteenth (number 16) letter in the English alphabet. ==History== Phoenician P Archaic Greek Pi Greek Pi Cyrillic Pe Etruscan P Latin P == Meanings for P == * In chemistry, P is the symbol for the element phosphorus, or sometimes for phosphate. * In chess, P is sometimes used as a symbol for the pawn piece. * In American football, P is used as a symbol for the punter. * ==Related pages== * Pi (mathematical constant) ==Other websites==
